observations.recommendation:
We recommended to the Municipal Mayor to create an Inventory Committee and:
a.) require the Inventory Committee to conduct an inventory under its jurisdiction, prepare and submit a verified Report on the Physical Count of the Road Network System (RPCRNS);
b.) direct the General Services Officer, Municipal Accountant to reconcile records between offices; 
c.) require all officers concerned to strictly comply to Section 189 of GAM for LGUs by preparing the RIS and RSMI and posting disclosures on the LGU website.

We recommended to the Municipal Mayor to:
a.) direct the Property Officer and the Accountant to reconcile its records and determine the causes of the variance for proper disposition thereof; 
b.) direct the Property Officer to maintain property cards with complete historical data.
